data.description: Welcome! This 3-bed, 2-bath, split-level home is waiting for your personal touch! This charming property features 3 bedrooms on the top floor with an en-suite bathroom in the master. There is a sizeable backyard complete with a large porch giving the perfect space for outdoor enjoyment and entertaining. This home is a fantastic starter opportunity and invites creativity or a personalized renovation. Don't miss the  chance to turn this into your dream home - a cozy heaven in Lothonia's heart.
